high_descs: Turn and go to the tvstand under the tv.
Pick up the yellow item that looks like a knife.
Turn right and go into the bathroom that is ahead on your left.
Put the knife in the sink, rinse it off and take it out.
Turn and leave the room and go to the coffeetable in front of the couch.
Put the knife on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off the knife and put it on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Turn right to face the counter under the tvstand.
Pick the knife from the counter.
Turn left and walk into the bathroom on the left to face the sink.
Rinse the knife in the sink and take it out.
Turn left to exit the bathroom and turn right to reach the coffeetable on the left.
Put the knife on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Knife on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Turn around turn right go straight to the tv stand
Take the knife from the tv stand
Turn left go straight turn right to the Sink
Put the knife in the sink clean it and take it back
Turn left go straight turn right to the coffee table
Place the knife on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Take the knife from the tv stand and Place the knife on the coffee table
